verbose_text: This unsupervised differential expression analysis led us to denote the small cluster NMF1 as " Matrix "-expressing cells based on their expression of mesenchymal / matrix related transcripts (e.g., Coll, 3, 5, 6, 12, 15, 18; Fn1; Vim), and to denote NMF4 as " lmmune "-related cells based on their expression of class II transcripts (e.g., B2m; Fcerlg; H2-Aa, Ab1, Eb1, M2, Q6, Q7, T22) (XREF_FIG).
